&lt;p>In 2015 Cambridge University scientists discovered that myelin cannot repair itself without a healthy daily supply of vitamin D3. Long term studies reveal that MS patients who receive a healthy daily dose of Vitamin D3 suffer significantly less disability and have MRI&amp;rsquo;s scans with fewer lesions when compared with MS patients with low blood levels of Vitamin D3. Now for the first time, thousands of MS patients are halting and reversing their disease with high doses of vitamin D3 and magnesium.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Breast Cancer death 1.8 X more likely if poor vitamin D Receptor</title><link>//localhost:1313/posts/breast-cancer-death-18-x-more-likely-if-poor-vitamin-d-receptor.html</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/posts/breast-cancer-death-18-x-more-likely-if-poor-vitamin-d-receptor.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>Autistic irritability reduced by Vitamin D plus Omega-3 – RCT</title><link>//localhost:1313/posts/autistic-irritability-reduced-by-vitamin-d-plus-omega-3-rct.html</link><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/posts/autistic-irritability-reduced-by-vitamin-d-plus-omega-3-rct.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>Vitamin D (calcitriol) reduces ability of cancer cells from becoming drug resistant</title><link>//localhost:1313/posts/vitamin-d-calcitriol-reduces-ability-of-cancer-cells-from-becoming-drug-resistant.html</link><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/posts/vitamin-d-calcitriol-reduces-ability-of-cancer-cells-from-becoming-drug-resistant.html</guid><description/></item><item><title>First trimester UV (probably also Vitamin D) associated with many later health benefits</title><link>//localhost:1313/posts/first-trimester-uv-probably-also-vitamin-d-associated-with-many-later-health-benefits.html</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/posts/first-trim